                    	<p>Ispahani Public School & College, Comilla commonly referred to as IPSC is a well known private educational institution on Comilla,Bangladesh. The institution offers primary, secondary and higher secondary education facilities under the Comilla Education Board. Founded by Mirza Ahmad Ispahani in 1979 the institution is widely known for its excellent results in S.S.C. and H.S.C. exams and its discipline.</p>
